'''Aiai''' ('''A'''dministrative, '''I'''nteractive '''A'''ssistance over '''I'''nternet) is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] administration tool and aid for [[disability|disabled people]] who require personal assistance. The [[software]] tool is used by both assistants and the clients or a company managing the assistance.
Aiai supports and is driven by and based on the [[Independent Living]] philosophy.
== External links == [https://www.aiai.se Aiai homepage]
